OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright morning with
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine. Sikes will become
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy this afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some patchy rain arriving later.
OL,9,FTemperatures around average with
OL,10,Flighter winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy and damp evening
OL,13,Fwith further spells of rain and
OL,14,Fdrizzle. Some drier and clearer
OL,15,Fintervals developing overnight, but
OL,16,Fdrizzle continuing over the hills.
OL,17,FMild with winds strengthening later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
