OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome early brightness
OL,6,Fpossible, before a band of heavy rain
OL,7,Fmoves eastwards. Turning drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter later in the day with winds
OL,9,Falso gradually easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Flargely fine and dry weekend as high
OL,13,Fpressure builds in. Feeling pleasant
OL,14,Fin any sunshine and lighter winds.
OL,15,FLikely to remain similar early next
OL,16,Fweek as high pressure dominates.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
